# Omninuera
**Role:** AI Intern

Date: [Start Date]

Candidate: **[Candidate Full Name]**

Dear [Candidate Full Name],

We are pleased to offer you a temporary internship position with Omninuera in the role of AI Intern. This offer outlines the key terms of the internship and is editable as needed.

## Position Details
- Duration: 3 months.
- Stipend: INR 10,000 per month (labelled 'stipend').
- Location: Fully remote; candidate based in Bengaluru.
- Engagement type: Internship / temporary engagement. This is not an employment contract and does not, by default, entitle the candidate to employee benefits unless explicitly stated in writing by Omninuera.
- Expected weekly commitment: 20–40 hours per week (flexible scheduling to support remote work).
- Reporting Manager: [Reporting Manager]

## Key Responsibilities
The AI Intern will be expected to undertake the following responsibilities:
- Data preparation and cleaning for machine learning experiments.
- Setting up and running model experiments and training pipelines.
- Evaluating model performance and producing quantitative and qualitative analyses.
- Documenting experiments, methodologies, and results in a clear, reproducible manner.
- Collaborating with the team to integrate feedback, participate in meetings, and contribute to project planning.

## Confidentiality and Intellectual Property
- The candidate acknowledges that during the internship they may receive access to confidential, proprietary, or sensitive information belonging to Omninuera, its clients, or partners.
- The candidate agrees to keep all such information strictly confidential during and after the internship and not to disclose it to any third party without prior written consent from Omninuera.
- All inventions, discoveries, designs, developments, works of authorship, improvements, and other intellectual property (whether or not patentable or copyrightable) that the candidate conceives, creates, reduces to practice, or authors, either alone or jointly with others, during the course of the internship and which relate to Omninuera's business or actual or demonstrably anticipated research and development, shall be the sole and exclusive property of Omninuera.
- The candidate hereby assigns to Omninuera all right, title, and interest in and to such intellectual property and agrees to execute any documents necessary to effectuate such assignment.

## Termination and Early Exit
- Either party may terminate this internship engagement by providing one (1) week written notice to the other party.
- Omninuera reserves the right to terminate the internship immediately for cause, including but not limited to breach of confidentiality obligations, misconduct, gross negligence, or violation of Omninuera policies.

## Stipend Payment Schedule
- The stipend of INR 10,000 per month will be paid monthly by bank transfer.
- Please provide bank details for stipend payment: [Bank Account Details for Stipend].
- Payments will be processed following receipt of any required documentation and in accordance with Omninuera payroll procedures.

## Conditions
- This offer is subject to completion of any required legal compliance review and satisfactory background verification (if applicable).
- The offer is conditional upon the candidate providing any requested documents and complying with Omninuera’s onboarding procedures.

## Governing Law and Jurisdiction
- This agreement and any disputes arising from it shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws applicable in Bengaluru, India. The parties submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Bengaluru, India for any disputes arising out of or relating to this offer.

